# Cylindrical Coordinate 3D Visualizer with Stable Camera

An interactive Streamlit application for visualizing points and cylindrical surfaces in the cylindrical coordinate system \((r, \phi, z)\).  
This tool allows real-time adjustment of the radius, angular coordinate, and height, while preserving the 3D camera angle during user interactions.

